What you need to know:

The Odinga visit scheduled for October 30 at the Nyeri Kabiru-ini ASK grounds next to Dedan Kimathi University will be the first public rally by the former PM since the sensational “Handshake” of March 9, 2018 between him and President Uhuru Kenyatta.But the tour, and subsequent announcement that Mr Odinga would make a reciprocal visit for a public rally in Nyeri, has ignited vicious attacks against the Kiago group by rival lobbies.